snippet.title: UNUSUAL PETS are so SUPER FUNNY & CUTE - Are you ready to SCREAM WITH LAUGHTER?
snippet.description:
These unusual pets are so super funny and cute. I'm sure they won't fail to make you laugh! This compilation is the most impossible try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look how all these lamas, monkeys, armadillos, parrots, skunks... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this compilation is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun

MUSIC:
"Monkeys Spinnin Monkeys" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
